<eesti> I LISA </eesti>
<inglise> The pilot computerized system was designed with a view to monitoring Aujeszky's disease. </inglise>
<eesti> Elektrooniline katses&uuml;steem on loodud Aujeszky haiguse j&auml;relevalveks. </eesti>
<inglise> It provides a trial for the introduction of a standardized animal-health management system for areas with a high livestock density. </inglise>
<eesti> Selle abil saadakse kogemusi standarditud veterinaarkorralduse s&uuml;steemi kasutuselev&otilde;tmises piirkondades, kus on k&otilde;rge loomkoormus. </eesti>
<inglise> The design selected for the computerized information system could serve as reference basis for the development of database systems for livestock records and movements. </inglise>
<eesti> Automatiseeritud infos&uuml;steem v&otilde;iks toimida loomade registri ja liikumise andmebaasis&uuml;steemide arendamisel v&otilde;rdlusalusena. </eesti>
<inglise> The project is in line with the measure for the identification of livestock and the tracing of livestock movements with a view to monitoring animal health and helping to improve the animal-health status of holdings. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev projekt on koosk&otilde;las meetmega, mis k&auml;sitleb loomade kindlakstegemist ja nende liikumise j&auml;lgimist, pidades silmas loomade tervisliku seisundi j&auml;lgimist ja p&otilde;llumajandusettev&otilde;tete loomade tervisliku seisundi parandamist. </eesti>
